OL,4,G1400FArt's Wildest Movement: Mannerism
OL,5,     GGoodbye Renaissance: Waldemar
OL,6,     GJanuszczak drills to the heart of
OL,7,     GMannerism, asking when did it
OL,8,     Ghappen, what were its
OL,9,     Gcharacteristics and what did it
OL,10,     Gachieve?
